Sand Framework
Sand Framework is a comprehensive platform for Solana developers and Web3 enthusiasts, combining a distributed multi-agent system with AI-driven tools, automated smart contract analysis, real-time blockchain analytics, and collaborative features. It features an AI-powered development assistant, automated security scanning for smart contracts, real-time analytics (price tracking & sentiment), and seamless Discord integration ‚Äì all architected for scalability and ease of use‚Äã
